Package edu.iit.sat.itmd4515.dhalmy.domain

Class Monitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.iit.sat.itmd4515.dhalmy.domain.Monitor
  • @Entity
public class Monitor
extends Object
    Represents a monitor within the organization. Each monitor is uniquely identified by an ID and has attributes such as asset tag, serial number, make and model, and an associated cubicle (location).
    Author:
    David
